<section xml:id="soc" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0">
    <title>Summary of changes</title>
    <section>
        <title>Version 4 LTS - 5 LTS</title>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in product:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-sources-internal"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-global-hostname"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-agent-mark-messages"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-agent-flow-control"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-agent-eventlog-api"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-sources-eventlog-add"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-install-silent"/> has been updated.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-macros"/> has been updated.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of <trademark>RLTP</trademark> has been added to <xref linkend="windows-configure-destination"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of using SDATA has been changed in <xref linkend="windows-configure-destination"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Option <guimenu>Read Old Records</guimenu> has been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The command line option <parameter>/d</parameter> has been changed, and <parameter>/e</parameter> has been removed from <xref linkend="windows-command-line"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="windows-debug-logging"/> has been updated. Debug logging now uses a <filename>.ini</filename> file.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The obsolete option <guimenu>Force DNS Hostname</guimenu> has been deleted from <xref linkend="chapter-windows-troubleshooting"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The obsolete <guimenu>Last Modified File Only</guimenu> and <guimenu>IIS 5.x Log</guimenu> options have been deleted from <xref linkend="windows-sources-file"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The obsolete <guimenu>EventData (deprecated Agent v3.1 functionality)</guimenu> and <guimenu>Agent v3.1 Snare Compatible Message Type (deprecated)</guimenu> options have been deleted from <xref linkend="windows-sources-eventlog"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The obsolete <guimenu>Set Primary Server</guimenu> option has been deleted from <xref linkend="chapter-destinations"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Figures <emphasis>Adding new server</emphasis>, <emphasis>Legacy BSD Syslog Protocol</emphasis>, <emphasis>Syslog Protocol</emphasis>, <emphasis>Snare Protocol</emphasis>, <emphasis>Failover Servers</emphasis> and <emphasis>Managing file sources</emphasis> have been updated.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in document:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><emphasis>Chapter 3, Configuring the &agentabbrev;</emphasis> has been split to separate chapters.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </section>
</section>
